node.text:
Crystal, a Community Engagement Coordinator for @savethechildren, is bringing hope to those in her Tennessee community with help from P&G and @safeguardsoap. 

Crystal’s story is one example of how we’re stepping forward to #LeadWithLove. Thanks to our partner @katiecouric for sharing her story! #LeadWithLove
Thank you for all you have done ✌❤🌎
Thank you for all you have done ✌❤🌎

shortcode_media.title: Crystal and Save the Children Are Impacting Lives in Rural Tennesse
